!   mqtt.ecs

    script MQTTTest

    use plugin MQTT from ec_mqtt

    topic Request
    topic Response
    
    init Request
        name `38:54:39:34:62:d7/request`
        qos 1
    init Response
        name `38:54:39:34:62:d7/response`
        qos 1

    mqtt
        id `EasyCoder-MQTT-Test`
        broker `test.mosquitto.org`
        port 1883
        topics Response
    
    on mqtt message log the mqtt message

    wait 3
    
    send mqtt `Hello, World!` to Request

    wait 3

    exit
